Package org.jcatapult.mvc.action.result

Interface Summary
Result<T extends Annotation> This interface defines the public API for the result.
ResultInvocation This class models the information necessary to invoke a result.
ResultInvocationProvider This interface defines the mechanism used to load and cache results.
ResultProvider This interface defines the provider that creates Results.
 

Class Summary
AbstractResult<U extends Annotation> This result performs a servlet forward to a JSP or renders a FreeMarker template depending on the extension of the page.
ControlHashModel This class is a hash that stores the Control classes so that they can be used from the FreeMarker templates.
DefaultResultInvocation This class is the default result invocation.
DefaultResultInvocationProvider This class is the default implementation of the result provider.
DefaultResultProvider This class is the manager for all the Results.
ForwardResult This result performs a servlet forward to a JSP or renders a FreeMarker template depending on the extension of the page.
ForwardResult.ForwardImpl  
RedirectResult This result performs a HTTP redirect to a URL.
RedirectResult.RedirectImpl  
ResultHttpServletRequest This class is a servlet request wrapper that interacts with the expression evaluator in order to pull out attributes from the action.
StreamResult This result performs a HTTP redirect to a URL.
